name: Charm Medal
description: Medal awarded for selling certain weapons and nightmares, and for participating in the Colosseum.

name: Gran Medal
description: Medal awarded to those who excel in the Gran Colosseum. Can be exchanged for rare treasures.

name: Friend Medal
description: Medals bestowed upon those who have forged the truest friendships. Earned by joining co-op battles with friends/guild members.

name: +EXP Vial
description: Doubles EXP earned during the story for 30 minutes.
noticeDescription: Note: If this item is already in effect,\nits duration will be overwritten and set to 30 minutes.

name: +Drop Vial
description: Doubles item drop rates during the story for 30 minutes.
noticeDescription: Note: If this item is already in effect,\nits duration will be overwritten and set to 30 minutes.

name: +Gold Vial
description: Doubles gold earned during the story for 30 minutes.
noticeDescription: Note: If this item is already in effect,\nits duration will be overwritten and set to 30 minutes.

name: Purification Ticket
description: Show this ticket to purify at any time.

name: Book of Opportunity
description: Introductory class handbook. Awards 5,000 class mastery.

name: Book of Destruction
description: Basic class handbook. Awards 10,000 class mastery.

name: Book of Crisis
description: Practical class handbook. Awards 25,000 class mastery.

name: Book of Completion
description: In-depth class guide. Awards 50,000 class mastery.

name: Dragon Claw (Fire)
description: Material for evolving weapons. Fuse with a weapon to release a subtle magical force.

name: Dragon Scale (Fire)
description: Material for evolving weapons. Its magic can be transferred to a weapon.

name: Dragon Eye (Fire)
description: Materials for evolving weapons. Its magic can only transfer to a weapon that has spilt blood...and lots of it.

name: Bird Feather
description: Material for evolving armor. A bird's feather that endows armor with minor protection.

name: Bird Wing
description: Material for evolving armor. Boosts armor in the main story.

name: Bird Crown
description: Material for evolving armor. A bird's crown found only on long-lived birds. Unleashes hidden power within the armor.

name: Bird Mask
description: Material for evolving armor. The mask of a cannibalistic bird. Unleashes hidden power within the armor.

name: Beast Oil
description: Material for evolving nightmares. A priceless liquid valued across the Library's many lands for its magical properties.

name: Plant Mucus
description: Material for evolving nightmares. A mucus secreted by region-specific plants when they sense danger.

name: Fresh Serpent Blood
description: Material for evolving nightmares. The divine blood of a serpent worshipped by characters in the story.

name: Fresh Dragon Blood
description: Material for evolving nightmares. The blood of a unique type of dragon. Very difficult to obtain since dragons vanish upon death.
